div.div: SSS-geup Teukseongeul Badatjiman Jeokdanghi Salgo Sipda

The world now swarms with supernatural beings called Celestials and the Awakened, people with newfound special powers. But none of this means anything to Yoo Sungwon, an ordinary man trying to live an ordinary life. Unfortunately for him, his peaceful days end when he gets a mysterious text and becomes a rare SSS-class knight with perks to die for. In order to avoid getting killed or targeted by those who want his powers for their own, Sungwon has no choice but to get stronger by leveling up.
(Source: Tapas)

With the unexplained emergence of dungeons came a relentless onslaught of monsters that overwhelmed humanity. Even the Awakened, humans with special abilities to fight monsters, couldn’t stop the destruction of the world. In the end, only Seong-In Kim, the most powerful Awakened, was left standing. Upon his death, Seong-In wakes up twenty years in the past as an unassuming high school student named Su-Hyeon Kim. He’s not sure how or why he was brought back, but he does know this is his second chance to save the world and redeem himself as a hero. (Source: Tapas, edited)
